g.text: Renewable Energy Landscape in the European Union
European Union Countries by Share of Primary Energy from Renewable Sources in 2023, Grouped by Regions

This visualization presents European Union countries categorized by regions, highlighting the share of primary energy from renewable sources in 2023. For each country, it displays detailed information including the region, population, the share of primary energy derived from renewables, and per capita renewable energy consumption.
Area of the circle = population in 2023 *
